# FlowTyme client rules

## Page responsibilities

- `Dashboard`: date selection + “Generate Plan” (calls server pipeline).
- `Proposals`: day-view timeline with drag-and-drop edits; conflict resolution happens here.
- `Confirm`: summary + final push to iCloud.
- `Setup`: edits runtime config stored in MongoDB.

## API usage

- Prefer using `client/src/api.ts` for server calls, not ad-hoc `fetch`.
- Types live in `client/src/types.ts`; keep request/response shapes aligned with server routes.

## react-big-calendar styling

- react-big-calendar CSS fights Tailwind. Prefer CSS var overrides in `client/src/index.css` (dark theme via vars).

## Category colors

- There is a static `CATEGORY_COLORS` map used in the proposals UI; unknown categories fall back to a muted color.

